name: To The Mooooon: The Milky Way
name_original: To The Mooooon: The Milky Way
description:
FULL-SCREEN GAME FOR BEST RESULTS!

This is a stealth game where you play as a cow named Milkshake that gets abducted by aliens. Try not to get caught as you work your way through the levels to take over the ship with your cow friend!

--

This is my fourth game for CS3540 - Game Programming class at Northeastern University. This was my final project which I made with 3 others. It was made completely in Unity and GitHub.
